name: Meditation
description:
Have you ever tried meditation? calm, clear the mind, create nothing, play with the subconscious. and the most impressive thing is talking to yourself to make peace with yourself? ever?
If you haven't tried it yet, do so right away, because meditating with a blank mind will give you answers you can't find anywhere else. if you have tried it, increase your meditation until you find a comfortable place other than the real world and the virtual world.

even when your concentration is high, you can find something really extraordinary like macro cosmos and micro cosmos
